      <abstract id="aspace_3e5ae16b9c82b4ebb02ac782e2169fd7">The records include minutes, reports, correspondence, and election results of the Brooklyn City Library spanning the period 1839 to 1843. The Brooklyn City Library was a subscription library incorporated in 1839 and located in the Brooklyn Lyceum Building, where it operated until 1851.</abstract>
